'''Ursu n ureɣ''' (s [[Talmant|telmant]] ''Goldener Bär'') d [[arraz]] yettunefken deg [[Taberlinit|Tafaska n Berlin]] seg [[1951]]. Yettunefk sɣur amgalaw unṣib i [[asaru|wsaru]] aɣezfan n timenyagert tagraɣlant. Ursu d [[azamul]] n tamdint n [[Berlin]]. 

Ursu n ureɣ yetsreɣɣet sɣur [[Renée Sintenis]]. 

Ar ass agi, ala imseḍru [[Taywan|ataywan]] [[Ang Lee]] i yernan (i rebḥen) ursu n ureɣ snat tikkwal (deg 1993 d 1996).
